fields.description: Features Of the UnbornHeart: Smartphone app allows you to monitor your babies heart rate Sleek Stylish, ultra compact design Connect your smart phone to monitor your babies progress Designed for comfort and ease of use Compare the data and track your babies progress Ultrasonic receiver picks up the slightest sound Listen to your unborn babys beating heart Play your babys heart beat through your phones loudspeaker Record, playback and share live audio clips of your babies heart Headphones for listening in directly Ultrasound gel, batteries, headphones and user friendly guide all included The UnbornHeart Smartphone Fetal Doppler has revolutionized the way new parents can listen and share the precious sound of their unborn babies heart beat intimately with family and friends. Not only does the unborn heart allow you to listen in to those precious beats but it gives unparalleled access to data previously only available in the hospital. And it does this all through your Smartphone! The UnbornHeart consists of two components, the handset and the smartphone. The handsets unique designs is ultra-compact and extremely easy to use, the back of the handset encompasses the ultra-sonic Doppler receive. The receiver has been designed to ensure it sits at the correct angle on your baby bump and can easily be moved around to find the heart beat in different areas using the chemical free ultrasound gel included. You will also find on the side of the control unit there is an adapter slot, this enables you to connect your smart phone through the head phone jack to use the Unborn Hearts Unique Feature. Plugging in your smart phone unveils a whole new perspective on fetal heart monitoring. The Free Unborn Heart App is dedicated only to this devices and give tracking you data normally only available during your hospital scans The Unborn Heart Doppler and App allow you to monitor your babys heart rate and watch it in real time using the graph in the app The data inside the app can feedback a trend chart so you can monitor day by day or week by week as the heart beat gets stronger and track the development of your baby. The app also allows you to record, share store the sound recordings and play them back to friends and family or even share them via email, text message and social media. Using your smartphone also allows you to amplify the sound from the monitor and use it as a loud speaker so you and your partner or even your family can all hear the beautiful sound of your babys heartbeat. If however you would like more privacy then you can use the headphones included or even your own to have a close listen to your baby as there heart beats in time, we recommend a good set of headphones to really get the best quality audio output. Everything you need to start monitoring your babies heart beat comes with the monitor in the pack, this includes the monitor itself, a set of headphones, the cable needed to connect your smart phone, the Unborn heart ultrasound gel, a set of batteries and a complete user friend instruction guide. Age Group: Infant.
fields.name: UnbornHeart Smartphone Fetal Heart Doppler

fields.description: Introducing the KitSound Sound Stand The KS Sound Stand is a lightweight, portable speaker which provides surround sound either on the move or as a smart desktop stand. High Quality Surround Sound Because he wanted his audiences to feel as though the orchestra was actually in the theatre with them, Walt Disney gave cinema-goers a completely new, immersive film-viewing experience by using surround sound in his 1940 film Fantasia. 70 years on and the KS Sound Stand, lets you watch films and listen to music in surround sound on your tablet or mobile. And thanks to both its twin dynamic Neodymium speakers which increase efficiency, lower distortion and have a high output and Sound Retrieval System (SRS) technology which creates a more spacious sense of ambience and makes more of discrete instruments, you can rest assured that your media is being given the platform it deserves. Create Your Own Home Cinema System If you love watching films in surround sound, the Sound Stand is ideal for when youre away from home, especially considering your device can be positioned at a comfortable angle for either landscape or portrait viewing. Ultra Light and Portable Not only do the Sound Stands Neodymium speakers make for a speaker system which is lightweight and comfortable to carry, but its foldable wings and adjustable clips hold your device firmly in place to provide a stable desktop stand. You could even take inspiration from the Swedish Lunch Beat events and have an hour-long rave at lunchtime. Although your work colleagues might not be so happy about that. Unless of course theyre from Sweden. Compatible and Long-Lasting The Sound Stands 3.5 mm jack and stereo cable ensure easy connection to most portable audio devices, so you can have surround sound whether youve got an iPhone, iPod Touch, iPad, tablet or smartphone. And because the built-in battery - which lasts for up to 4 hours - takes just 2 hours to recharge by plugging the supplied USB cable into a laptop, USB mains charger or USB car charger, you can spend less time waiting to hear your tunes and more time listening to them. About KitSound We are craftspeople. We are musicians. We are KitSound and we all commit ourselves to achieving one shared goal: Bringing people closer to their music. By understanding music we stay true to its craft. Pure, rich, incredible sound. We settle for nothing less. Specifications: Play time: up to 4 hours Drivers: 2 x 30 mm NdFeb S/N: 78 dB Frequency response: 80 Hz - 17.5 kHz Jack socket: 3.5 mm Surround engine: SRS
fields.name: Tablet and Smartphone Surround Sound Sound Stand, KitSound

fields.description: Ideal for low light and portraits, this ultra-bright lens produces beautiful bokeh and wonderful, professional-looking photos that pop with clarity and detail. The G4s state-of-the-art, infrared-sensitive colour spectrum sensor analyzes and measures all of the visible light within a scene before a shot is snapped, ensuring that an images colours appear natural and vivid even in dim conditions. Turn every moment into a work of art by adjusting camera settings that tweak lightness and darkness, freeze movement faster, and allow for better low-light shooting. With the G4s manual mode, you can set your camera to easily and artfully capture the blazing lights. Snap quick and clear pictures with the G4s laser detection auto-focus, and OIS 2.0, an improved optical image stabiliser that reduces camera shake. Ideal for capturing that perfect selfie, this top-of-the-line 8MP front shooter utilizes LGs fun and convenient Gesture Shot and Gesture View features. The IPS Quantum Display produces high-contrast, vibrant images that are rich and authentic in colour and amazingly true-to-life. It also benefits from In-cell Touch Display technology, which provides a smooth and super-responsive feel at the same time as making the screen easily visible in daylight. Inspired by artisanal precision, the G4s premium back covers come in metallic gray, ceramic white, gold, and genuine leather. The chic coloured backs are distinguished by a textural hammered-array pattern while the classic leather option is available in a number of distinct colours and features an exquisite threaded stitch. The G4s durable slim arc design allows for a natural, firm grip and was created with the ideal user experience in mind. Size: L. Color: Grey. Pattern: Metallic. Material: Leather.
fields.name: G4 H815 (5.5 inch) Smartphone Snapdragon (808) 3GB RAM 32gb eMMC (Metallic Grey), LG

fields.description: The compact yet premium design of the LG G3 S comes with a uniquely curved design for a better grip and metallic skin for minimalizing smudges. The arc shaped design makes the sides much thinner, allowing easy one-hand control. Enjoy life-like colours on the screen that is just the right size for everyday viewing excitement. Not only dose the OIS(Optical Image Stabilization) function reduce blur and shaking, the laser measures the distance to the object instantly, giving you perfect quality photos with 8MP. You can also take brighter, clearer pictures even in dark conditions. With its quick focus adjustment, you will never miss a moment you want to capture. Unnecessary icons on the screen have been eliminated to give you a clear view. Plus, it simplifies the process of taking shots. Now simply get a focus and take a perfect shot with just one touch. The long battery life ensures that youll find the power you need to perform any task all through your day. Size: S/L. Color: Gold. Pattern: Metallic.
fields.name: G3 S D722 (5 inch) Smartphone with Android 4.4 KitKat (Gold), LG

fields.description: The new afforadable MultiPhone 5504 DUO lets you enjoy what matters most: advanced imaging, music, video, social networks and much more. You can engage different mobile networks on one phone and keep two lines for separate purposes, like private and business. Save money by using different price tariffs for calls and 3G. While travelling abroad stay in touch with your relatives still using a local SIM. Andoid 4. 4 (KitKat) has a more elaborate design, advanced performance and lots of up-to-date features. KitKat is super-smooth, the UI is refined and elegant. There are improvements to the long-neglected calling and messaging side of the platform. It is more focused on productivity. Brilliant 5. 0 IPS screen features the clearest picture quality. Perfect for comfortable reading, watching movies and web surfing. Color: Gunmetal.
